{comment: Verse 2}
[C]I was sitting in the bathtub counting my toes,
[F]when the radiator broke, water all froze.
[C]I got stuck in the ice without my clothes,
[G]naked as the eyes of a clown.

[C]I was crying ice cubes hoping I'd croak,
[F]when the sun come through the window, the ice all broke.
[C]I stood up and laughed, thought it was a joke
[G]That's the w[C]ay that the world goes 'round.

